lead_paragraph: Nathan Eovaldi of the New York Yankees had his no-hit bid against the Texas Rangers ended by Nomar Mazara's single leading off the seventh inning.

headline.print_headline: Yankees' Eovaldi Has No-Hit Bid Ended in Top of 7th at Texas
